snippet.title: Buzzfeed Senior Editor Kevin Smith Weighs in on the Amber Rose Slut Walk + Cash Money Lawsuit
snippet.description:
Senior Editor at Buzzfeed, Kevin Smith, joined us for a special Celebrity Wire on Sway in the Morning and gave his 2 cents about the biggest Celeb story in the news. But before getting to that -- he humbly-stunted by announcing Buzzfeed's worth of $1.5 BILLION.

Watch above as he talks about the bitter lawsuit between Lil Wayne, Drake, Nicki Minaj, Tyga -- and Cash Money. Along with Amber Rose's LA Slut Walk.
